\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10449094 AL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1991128\charrsid12588588 He w
as sixty-seven. When he died, he died on the twentieth of October - no, he died on the sixteenth of October in 1918 on the Wednesday and he was buried on the Sunday, and the railway went to walk at the funeral, in those days they buried on the Sunday, the
y don't now. He was buried on the Sunday afternoon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1927463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1991128\charrsid12588588 Where did he come from?
