He was working - he was working you see over sixty-five owing to the first war
. And he took pneumonia in 1918, and he died as I tell you, on those dates in - in - and - he was sixty-seven when he died. I think he'd be sixty-seven the previous September, the month before because - he used to say that September was the best month of 
the year because he was born in it. So he must have been sixty-seven, and just turned - into the - into October.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1927463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1991128\charrsid12588588 Did he ever do any casual or part time jobs as well, your father?
